name: Settling for Awesome
description: Raw laser vid taken in LaserLewDude's closet 4-15-21. Setup contains lasers, glass, mirrors and water. There is a custom airtrap marble in the back bowl w/water. Lasers used: 2 LaserCube 1W; homemade RGB laser projector through Lumia Rig to create the moving background 'aurora'. Individual laser modules: 2x 505nm (water green), 2x 638nm (red), 2x 488nm (pretty blue), 1 488nm through 33 degree line generator and 100 lines/mm diffraction grating to make blue lines in upper background. Track royalty free.
